Package: GERnews
Title: GERnews simplifies online media research 
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-02-23
Authors@R: c(person("Isabelle", "Bonenkamp", role = c("aut", "cre"),
            email = "i.bonenkamp@live.de"),
             person("Friedrike", "Preu", role = "ctb"))
Author: Isabelle Bonenkamp [aut, cre],
         Friedrike Preu [ctb],
Maintainer: Isabelle Bonenkamp <i.bonenkamp@live.det>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), nlme
Imports: 
      XML,
      httr,
      stringr,
      RCurl,
      ggplot2
Suggests: 
      testthat
Description: GERnews simplifies online media research. It allows to access the search engines of the German online newspapers Faz, Spiegel and Zeit in RStudio and thus enables the user to scrape headlines (and articles) from the online archives. Further, the package provides sorting and visualizing the extracted informations. 
